title: 160 - F9 Premiere
description: Todays ship is steered by Tone Diggz and this is the last show of F9 week. The boys open up this feel Good Friday with their weekend plans and then lead into the latest shows and movies they have most recently watched. The boys jump into the Pod FOD which covers their favorite PIXAR movies, a Transformers teas, and much much more from all around the internet. We send you off into the weekend with a wedding madlib in honor of our dear friend an co-worker Ty who is getting married this weekend. Don't forget to subscribe to YouTube.com/thepodpmi to watch full episodes of The Pod, and send your questions to @ThePodPMI on twitter and Instagram. We appreciate you all for listening, and hope you have an incredible weekend. We'll see you Wednesday.
